query:
/*+ NoHashJoin(a1 b q1 s t1 tq1 u1) */ select acc.location,
count(*)
from question AS q1
inner join tag_question AS tq1
on q1.id = tq1.question_id AND q1.view_count >= 100 AND q1.view_count <= 100000
inner join tag AS t1
on t1.id = tq1.tag_id AND t1.name IN ('addeventlistener',
'android-sdcard',
'asterisk',
'azure-ad-b2c',
'coded-ui-tests',
'database-performance',
'github-pages',
'joomla3.0',
'multi-tenant',
'protobuf-net',
'unmarshalling',
'velocity',
'wcf-ria-services',
'web.xml',
'windows-server-2008-r2')
inner join answer AS a1
on q1.id = a1.question_id
inner join site AS s
on s.site_id = t1.site_id AND s.site_id = a1.site_id AND s.site_id = q1.site_id AND s.site_id = tq1.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('stackoverflow')
inner join badge AS b
on s.site_id = b.site_id AND b.name IN ('Autobiographer',
'Citizen Patrol',
'Commentator',
'Constituent',
'Custodian',
'Excavator',
'Good Question',
'Nice Question',
'Popular Question',
'Self-Learner',
'Tumbleweed')
inner join so_user AS u1
on s.site_id = u1.site_id AND a1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND b.user_id = u1.id AND u1.downvotes >= 0 AND u1.downvotes <= 10
inner join account AS acc
on acc.id = u1.account_id group by acc.location order by count(*) desc LIMIT 100;
